reviews.snippet:
Deceptive pricing.

1. When you order your meal, they will force you to buy high priced drink (starting from ¥590 for cola) even if you don’t want to. After paying for additional high priced drinks; they did not serve the drinks till the time we were finished with our meals (15-20 min later). Once cola was delivered; it was without frizz & we had to return them to get  re-filled.

2. All menu items prices are listed but they have add ons without which the meal would not be complete which means additional ¥450-500 which you don’t see in the listed price initially.

3. We were served water at the beginning and we had to ask multiple times to get more water but the server was able to fill the water glass again after persistently asking just before we were about to leave.

4. Food quality was good.

誤解を招く価格設定

注文時に、希望していなくても高額なドリンク（コーラでさえ¥590〜）の注文を半ば強制されました。追加料金を支払ったにもかかわらず、ドリンクが提供されたのは食事を終えた15〜20分後でした。ようやく運ばれてきたコーラも炭酸が抜けており、再度入れ替えをお願いすることになりました。

メニューには各料理の価格が表示されていますが、実際には付け合わせなどが別料金（¥450〜¥500）で設定されており、それらを追加しなければ食事として成り立たない構成になっています。結果的に、表記価格だけでは済まない仕組みです。

最初に水が提供されましたが、追加でお願いしてもなかなか注ぎ足してもらえず、何度もお願いした末、ようやく退店直前になって再び注がれました。

料理の味は良好でした。
reviews.translated_snippet:
Deceptive pricing.

1. When you order your meal, they will force you to buy high priced drink (starting from ¥590 for cola) even if you don’t want to. After paying for additional high priced drinks; they did not serve the drinks till the time we were finished with our meals (15-20 min later). Once cola was delivered; it was without frizz & we had to return them to get re-filled.

2. All menu items prices are listed but they have add ons without which the meal would not be complete which means additional ¥450-500 which you don’t see in the listed price initially.

3. We were served water at the beginning and we had to ask multiple times to get more water but the server was able to fill the water glass again after persistently asking just before we were about to leave.

4. Food quality was good.

Misleading pricing

When ordering, we were forced to order expensive drinks (even cola was ¥590 and up) even if we didn’t want them. Despite paying extra, the drinks were not served until 15-20 minutes after we had finished our meal. When the cola was finally brought to us, it had flattened out, so we had to ask for another one.

The menu lists the price of each dish, but in reality, side dishes and other items are charged separately (¥450-¥500), and the meal would not be complete without adding them. In the end, the system is such that you can't just get by with the listed price.

Water was served at first, but even when we asked for more, it was difficult to get more. After asking several times, it was finally refilled just before we left.

The food tasted good.

response.snippet:
Thank you so much for taking the time to leave us a review on Google. We truly appreciate your feedback and would like to take a moment to address a few of your concerns for clarity:
	1.	In the Ebisu area, it is common for most restaurants to require at least one drink and one dish order per person during dinner service. Regarding the bottle we served, we sincerely apologize that it initially lacked fizz. As soon as we noticed, we replaced it with a new one for you.
	2.	We strive to be transparent with our pricing, and all topping prices are clearly listed on the menu. We believe our pricing for items like beef tongue and braised beef offers excellent value compared to others in the area. As a valued regular during lunchtime, please note that lunch and dinner menus (and prices) differ. You can always check our updated menu on Google. For a group of 8, we believe a dinner including drinks totaling ¥19,490 is a reasonable and competitive price for the Ebisu area.
	3.	We sincerely apologize for the delay in refilling your water. We will make sure to improve our attentiveness moving forward.
	4.	Thank you again for your honest feedback. It helps us grow and serve our customers better.

We look forward to welcoming you again and providing you with an even better experience on your next visit.

place_info.address: 600 Kamiyotsugi, Akiruno, Tokyo 197-0832, Japan

reviews.snippet:
Very good waterpark with very clean environment. Management is excellent. Ticket for one adult 3,900 yen.

Expect line for each ride to be at least 2+ hrs.

The whole park looks like a refugee camp as people bring in tents right in the morning and cover almost 90% of the area of the park.

To take a break, shaded areas come at a cost (probably additional 8,000 yen or more) as there is very little shaded area available for free.

Parking is additional 2000 yen for a car.

Lazy river has very few (maybe 10-12) floats so must bring in own floats if you want to enjoy lazy river or buy it from the shop for another 4,000 yen.

Lockers are for 600 yen (100 refundable). They are sufficient in number and spread all across the park. Suggest to use lockers towards the center of the park in order to be able to access them for using somethings during the day.

place_info.title: Tayto - Centaurus Mall
place_info.address: Food Court, The Centaurus Mall, F8 Jinnah Avenue, F 8/4 F-8, Islamabad, 44000, Pakistan

reviews.snippet:
Exquisite burgers @ #Tayto , beautiful ambiance, horrible service (you will have to physical get up & go to the counter even to get salt), extremely miser on sides like french fries (you get total 12 pieces of french fries & 2 onion rings with your meal). They have very stylish plates to serve the burgers / meals which are extremely small in size. As the burgers are very juicy; so you are bound to make a large mess around the table as the plate is mini sized.

The mint margarita would cost you Rs.399 as compared to an extremely sugary Pepsi for Rs. 99 so be careful what drink you order.

Overall 9/10 for the burger & ambiance but 3/10 for service, utensils (including serving plates and side orders.
